
 [Uni Donkey] CHANGES
==============================================================================


=== v0.1

* Thu Jul 25 2003 Tim Niemueller <tim@niemueller.de>
- New feature: downloading files with unavailable chunks are drawn red in files
  list
- Added commit ability
- New buffer framework (see mlbuffer.(c|h)). Makes life easier as buffer is
  now "more managed" than before. Less work in buffer-using code, moved to
  buffer itself
- changed mldonkey.(c|h) to use new buffer framework
- Files can be commited in "Downloaded" view
- Damnit! Some time ago I disabled many checks in my POSE. So when I gave the
  current alpha to Medha he got several bugs... These could be removed by
  rearranging some code. Where problems with not yet allocated or already
  removed memory chunks. Thanx Medha for pointing this out!

* Tue Jul 23 2003 Tim Niemueller <tim@niemueller.de>
- Various, forgot CHANGEs file...
- basic features working, infrastructure works
- can view downloading and downloaded files
- stats
- progress dialog now has own framework

* Wed Jul 09 2003 Tim Niemueller <tim@niemueller.de>
- CVS import, basic stuff is working
- Rewrote chunks gadget
- wrote webpage for nice CVS import :-)

* Tue Mar 12 2003 Tim Niemueller <tim@niemueller.de>
- First steps to get the net code in place.
- Using CVS now from the beginning now

* Tue Mar 12 2003 Tim Niemueller <tim@niemueller.de>
- Dev Session at Tob. Created project on Medha's pushing


